<span>Dear <%= @invitee.name %>,</span><br><br>

<p>On behalf of i2i Events Group, we welcome you to the CWIEME, 2013 - The World's largest International Coil Winding, Insulations & Electrical Manufacturing Exhibition. </p>

<p>To access CWIEME 2013 Mobile Website, follow these 5 easy steps:</p>


<p>
<ol>
  <li>From your smartphone, tablet, laptop, PC or any device, type http://cwieme2013.procialize.net (This is a mobile website, you will not need to download any app!)</li>
  <li><b>Enter your email as: <%= @invitee.email %></b></li>
  <li><b>Enter your password as: procialize </b></li>
  <li>You will be live on the CWIEME Mobile Website! </li>
  <li> REGISTER for the CWIEME 2013 and based on our SmartRecommender system we feel you might be interested in interacting with:</li>
</ol>




<ol>
  <% @user=User.find_by_email(@invitee.email) %>
     <% @user_new=Array.new %>
  <% if !@user.recommend.nil? %>
      <% @user.recommend.split(", " ).each do |r| %>
          <%#= @user_new<<User.find_by_name(r) %>
          <% @reco= User.find_by_name(r.strip)%>
          <% @user_new << @reco %>
          <li>
            <%= @reco.name.titlecase %>
            <% if !@reco.company.blank? %>
                from <%= @reco.company %>
            <% end %>
          </li>
      <% end %>
  <% end %>
</ol>

