<ol>
  <li>Search, find, message and set up meetings with other delegates </li>
  <li>Quickly connect with others based on industry/designation/company/location </li>
  <li>View other delegate's profiles, in order to form promising partnerships </li>
  <li>Communicate with others before, during and after events</li>
